00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:03,270
You have entered the Play-to-earn section.

2
00:00:04,110 --> 00:00:09,420
Instead of paying for an NFT, play a game and earn NFTs along the way.

3
00:00:10,170 --> 00:00:11,790
Axie Infinity

4
00:00:12,290 --> 00:00:18,650
First released in 2018, Axie Infinity is an online-based video game

5
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:21,680
developed by the Vietnamese studio Sky Mavis.

6
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:22,340
Using a gaming format called “play-to-earn,”

7
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:23,750
Axie Infinity leverages blockchain technology

8
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:25,190
to reward players with crypto for their contributions to the game.

9
00:00:25,210 --> 00:00:39,550
As you play, you earn, buy and breed characters called Axies.

10
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:42,340
These can be pitted against each other,

11
00:00:42,430 --> 00:00:47,680
in an effort to win in-game cash which can be exchanged for real money.

12
00:00:48,180 --> 00:00:56,580
Axie Infinity players can also purchase and sell virtual land and NFTs within the gaming platform.

13
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:06,330
As of March 2022, Axie Infinity NFTs have hit $4 billion in all-time sales.

14
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:11,280
Since its inception four year ago the play-to-earn format

15
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:14,670
continues to grow in size and engagement.

16
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:20,490
Players in the play-to-earn space can earn thousands of dollars a month,

17
00:01:20,730 --> 00:01:25,260
some leaving their full time jobs to play full time.

18
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:28,410
If a player needs financial investment,

19
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:33,540
investors have offered Axie scholarships to help players buy into the games,

20
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,240
and in turn, earn more money.

